ent-AU14HAZOPSclothingequipmentvendor = HAZOPS apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Hazardous Operations apparel of the Marine Special Operations Command. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14HAZOPSMGequipmentvendor = HAZOPS smartgunner equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated smartgunner rack, hooked up to a small armory of Hazardous Operations heavy-weapon operator systems of the Marine Special Operations Command. Standard issue for designated smart-gun crews on naval vessels and high-threat outposts. Built to bring heavy fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14HAZOPSWeaponsVendor = HAZOPS weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Hazardous Operations weaponry of the Marine Special Operations Command. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14HAZOPSSpecialWeaponsVendor = HAZOPS special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Hazardous Operations heavy and breaching ordnance of the Marine Special Operations Command. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14HAZOPScommandequipmentvendor = HAZOPS command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Hazardous Operations command-leadership equipment of the Marine Special Operations Command. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14HAZOPSsectionleaderequipmentvendor = HAZOPS section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Hazardous Operations section-leadership equipment of the Marine Special Operations Command. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14HAZOPSRequisitionVendor = HAZOPS automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
